01022 *entonces es contra pedido.                                                                   
b07  C                   IF        ((Not %FOUND(ZAQBAL00)) Or                                       
69095C* C5958                      (%FOUND(ZAQBAL00) And MBTCON = 1) Or                             
69095C                             (%FOUND(ZAQBAL00) And MBMTSO = 'MTO') Or                         
